<br>
I am posting here in hoping to get some info about this mysterious zone. I think besides VT, this zone is next most unknown to the majority of the EQers. <br>
<br>
I think this zone is favored towards casters as they can bind themselves in the PoM, so they only need to make the run through NToV only once. <br>
<br>
For melees, I used to know a monk who pay heaps of plat for locket of escape just to bind himself in PoM.<br>
<br>
My questions are:<br>
<br>
- Can a 65 cleric and 63 Warrior duo in this zone for exp and quest item?<br>
- is CR here bad? (I plan to have the cleric bound in this zone and do all the CR)<br>
- Is this zone worth all the fuss?<br>
<br>
I do not have other specific questions but just wanna hear any great experience you may have had regarding this zone <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
